<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ạ̹n qwty klmạ qlby yjwʿ</title>
<aka>ạ̹n qwty klmạ nfsy yjwʿ</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (ại̹nã qūtī kulãmā naf̊sī tajūʿ̊
 warajāyỉy ḥīna ạảdẖ̊rifu ạldũmūʿ̊
 wasalạmī kulãmā kẖaṭ̊buⁿ yarūʿ̊
 man̊ faday̱ naf̊sī mukẖalĩṣī yasūʿ̊)2

[V2]
 2- (hūa birĩy ại̹dẖ̊ ṭamat̊ faẘqī ạldẖũnūb̊
 hūa sit̊rī ại̹n̊ ʿalat̊ naf̊sī ạl̊ʿuyūb̊
 hūa nūrī kulãmā ạllãẙlu yawủwb̊
 man̊ faday̱ naf̊sī mukẖalĩṣī yasūʿ̊)2

[V3]
 3- (hūa rib̊ḥī ại̹n̊ kẖasir̊tu mālīa
 hūa ạảh̊lī ại̹n̊ ṭuriḥ̊tu nāyỉyạ
 hūa far̊ḥī ại̹n̊ gẖadaẘtu bākīạ
 man̊ faday̱ naf̊sī mukẖalĩṣī yasūʿ̊)2

[V4]
 4- (fī sukūnī wān̊firādī ạảl̊taqīh̊
 yam̊lạủ ạl̊qal̊ba hanāʾaⁿ wayurīh̊
 ḥubãhu ạlsãạmī wakam̊ lilnãf̊si fīh̊
 man̊ faday̱ naf̊sī mukẖalĩṣī yasūʿ̊)2

[V5]
 5- (hūa dẖukẖ̊rī fīhi kulũ mā ạảsẖāʾ̊
 yā lahu dẖukẖ̊raⁿạ gẖadā lī fī ạlsãmāʾ̊
 fah̊wa min̊ ạảj̊lī hunāka fī ạl̊ʿalạʾ̊
 man̊ faday̱ naf̊sī mukẖalĩṣī yasūʿ̊)2</lyrics>
<hymn_number>10431</hymn_number>
</song>